    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君！\n怜ちゃんの怪我はどうだった？",
      "startTime": 2.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "幸いなことに、大したことはありませんでした\n一通り検査は受けて、今は寮で休んでますよ",
      "startTime": 8.0359303672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……怪我はともかく過労気味だったので\nしばらくは安静にということでした",
      "startTime": 14.9799322605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "良かった\n……でも過労って、ここ最近練習し過ぎだったせいよね",
      "startTime": 20.1666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "心配だわ……寮に帰ったら\n遙子特製栄養ドリンクでも差し入れようかしら",
      "startTime": 30.4666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "料理上手な遙子さんなら心配ないと思いますけど……\n一応、材料を聞いてもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 38.4367578666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。まずはマムシに青汁、にんにくでしょ",
      "startTime": 41.2700911999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……それはやめておきましょう",
      "startTime": 48.9856921037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、もちろん冗談よ\n安心して少し気が緩んじゃったわね",
      "startTime": 54.5333336194,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}